column5: Crap - 3:30 is WAY TOO EARLY to be getting out of bed.  More to follow.  Jeeze.
Quit yer whinin' and go catch us some fish boy!
And here I was going to say it must be nice to sleep so late  Hope it was a good day  Maureen
424 .... It should be a no brainer out there today , good luck guys, looking forward to the posts
They'd better be good!  Aren't you guys back my now? Where are our pics???????  p.-
I just got home a half hour ago.  I've been up since 2:30am......too tired to write anything.  I think Solopaddler is handling the report....  Here's a teaser pic....a nice fall steelie.
Is that a marshmallow stuck in its lip?Hope y'all had a good trip. Joe
Joe...this is a trout...not a salmon....  But thanks for comin' out....
Cliff....thats not fair.....making me wait for the 'real' report...lol.  BTW....i'm up at 3:30 am tomorrow for a day on Lac Seul....cant wait.
oh man the teaser pic!!!  im gonna head up north in about 3hrs for some fall steelheads too.
Patience lad, these things take time  .
You guys had me going for a minute with MOE...I though the ministry of environment was involved and I got to go!  Can't wait to see the results

will somebody PLEASE post this report.  haha i have a feeling were in for an EPIC OFC.  Whenever a report takes this long it usually includes many many pictures (good ones) and some serious pen work by either moosebunk or Solo. In this case its solo and a whole lot of trout.   ...and you guys didnt stop by my rez on the way because??????  damn midterms.
